Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.10,0:00:24.41,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,因爲總是在倆人獨處的時光裏 說不出話來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.03,0:00:33.67,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,小小的KISS 讓時間就這樣 停止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.95,0:00:36.38,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Need your love tonight
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.83,0:00:48.73,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,與在探尋命運的瞬間 相遇的妳 倆人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.80,0:01:00.07,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,回想起 雪的home 妳的身影 逐漸變小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.35,0:01:07.16,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,我會永遠獻給妳喔 Winter Bell
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.44,0:01:11.96,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,窗邊堆積的白雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.91,0:01:24.05,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我倆更加接近喔 Day by day 此時 請緊緊地抱著我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.34,0:01:30.60,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,我會永遠獻給妳喔 Winter Bell
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.88,0:01:41.99,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,此時 請緊緊地抱著我 在星星降臨的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.50,0:21:23.70,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是等待  刺激的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.70,0:21:30.20,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,眼前所見的  全部是重要的所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.20,0:21:42.60,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,失去的東西是恐怖的  但我們之間還什麼也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.60,0:21:43.90,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah　yeah  yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.90,0:21:50.00,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在這藍藍的地球上  無限重複未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.00,0:21:55.10,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,can make me free　想要感覺這種跳動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.10,0:21:56.50,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah  yeah  yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.50,0:22:02.50,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,這個心情飛舞升起 染滿天空與大海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.50,0:22:12.30,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊抱住你 想要飛起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.90,0:22:15.10,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah  yeah  yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.10,0:22:21.20,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,這個心情飛舞升起 染滿天空與大海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.20,0:22:31.50,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊抱住你 想要飛起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.20,0:00:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏的是心中的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.70,0:00:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照耀兩人的是星星和雪花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.80,0:00:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於步美的想法 暗號解開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.70,0:00:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘是謎團的那傢伙是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.60,0:00:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透了真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.20,0:00:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個外表看似小孩 智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.00,0:00:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.40,0:01:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看完了Paul & Annie的動物表演的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.40,0:01:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救了因被錯認而被記者重重包圍的詹姆斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.30,0:01:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.20,0:02:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了接我們去飯店而去開車的詹姆斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.40,0:02:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然失去了蹤影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.00,0:02:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是留下了一個沾了血的手機鏈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.20,0:02:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來自芝加哥的男人(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.50,0:02:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P&A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.50,0:02:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.00,0:02:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掉在這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.20,0:02:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是詹姆斯先生留給我們犯人的線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.60,0:02:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.30,0:02:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手機鏈的P和&和A都沾著血 是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.80,0:02:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.80,0:02:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就回局裡調查一下這是不是真正的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.20,0:02:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那明天到警察局裡見呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.10,0:02:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.80,0:02:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 至少也要知道P&A的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.70,0:03:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P和A會不會是PAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.10,0:03:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是做麵包的店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.90,0:03:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說 麵包店什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.70,0:03:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在緊急關頭的情況下 要想傳遞PAN的資訊的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.00,0:03:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就應該直接把P和A一起染上血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.90,0:03:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個暗號應該把P和A分開來想比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P和A  P和A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.60,0:03:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,粉色和紅色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,角鬥和包子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.30,0:03:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦和訪問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.60,0:03:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手槍和暗殺者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.90,0:03:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.80,0:03:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 難道是說Parking Area嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.50,0:03:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 停車場嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.50,0:03:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在哪的停車場也不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.90,0:03:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.00,0:03:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說詹姆斯先生剛剛停車的停車場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.70,0:03:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許還留下其他的什麼線索呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.20,0:03:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 剛剛我也是這麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.60,0:03:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以先調查了一下 結果什麼也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.20,0:03:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.30,0:04:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死 怎麼想都不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.70,0:04:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就只能先在這周圍打聽一下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.90,0:04:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.90,0:04:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家分開打聽一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.30,0:04:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有誰看見這附近有帶著外國人的兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.40,0:04:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果發現了什麼的話 就用偵探徽章來聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.80,0:04:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.20,0:04:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.20,0:04:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼也找不到偵探徽章了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒掉到哪里嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.40,0:04:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛給詹姆斯先生看的時候還...啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.50,0:04:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 夏洛克·福爾摩斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.40,0:04:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.00,0:04:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的詹姆斯先生還拿著我的偵探徽章呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.80,0:04:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.20,0:04:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大概是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.40,0:04:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.60,0:04:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就用徽章裡面裝的發信器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.70,0:04:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的位置是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.00,0:04:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡往北距離16公里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.50,0:05:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正沿著泰晤士街道開始北上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從速度來看的話應該是汽車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是汽車嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.50,0:05:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰晤士街道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.90,0:05:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.50,0:05:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.70,0:05:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道了這個的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.30,0:05:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你以為你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.90,0:05:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在幾門街道和崎玉縣的縣界之間進行盤查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以的 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.40,0:05:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,憑著這麼模糊的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.00,0:05:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就進行盤查的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.30,0:05:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個外國人有可能會被殺掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.10,0:05:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 呀 但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.70,0:05:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.20,0:05:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是佐藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.50,0:05:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在那邊正好發生交通事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由美正在進行交通疏導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.30,0:05:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要確認可疑的人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以拜託給她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.00,0:05:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身高大約180公分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五 六十歲左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.60,0:06:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶眼鏡 長鬍子 操英國口音的美國人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.30,0:06:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人乘坐的車子 是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果發現了這輛車的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.40,0:06:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上進行調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.00,0:06:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 犯人可能攜帶武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.40,0:06:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.40,0:06:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和高木警官馬上就過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.50,0:06:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.80,0:06:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.30,0:06:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.10,0:06:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我們到晚上為止都有空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.80,0:06:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且和那個孩子有關的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像都挺有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.40,0:06:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.30,0:06:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣 我們也去 博士把車子開過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.70,0:06:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我們才能確認詹姆斯先生的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.80,0:06:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有一點懷疑嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.30,0:06:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯先生和兩個男人從停車場穿過小巷到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乘了另一輛車的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個血的暗號應該是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.50,0:07:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在小巷裡面走的時候割破自己的手指留下的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.10,0:07:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃 應該是在停車場的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.40,0:07:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被兩個男人用手槍什麼的威脅著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.80,0:07:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後瞞著那兩個男人偷偷留下的暗號吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.40,0:07:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.50,0:07:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是明知道是可疑人物還特意跟著去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.10,0:07:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並給我們留下了資訊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.70,0:07:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你想說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.90,0:07:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被別人牽著鼻子走的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.40,0:07:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想的太多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.40,0:07:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是這樣就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.50,0:07:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看見了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.90,0:07:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛車裡坐的人的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.40,0:07:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太快了 沒看見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.50,0:07:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.90,0:08:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.90,0:08:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是外國人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.40,0:08:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.80,0:08:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外國人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.60,0:08:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外國人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.10,0:08:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外國人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.10,0:08:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 過來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.00,0:08:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.90,0:08:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 能不能讓我們先過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.70,0:08:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天黑之前必須和這個人做現場驗證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.40,0:08:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你們辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.30,0:08:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在情人的房間裡胡鬧的小氣傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.90,0:09:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.70,0:09:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.80,0:09:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外國人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.50,0:09:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是外國人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.90,0:09:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外國人一個也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.60,0:09:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在車子在什麼地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這前面8公里處移動中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.60,0:09:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快沒電了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.20,0:09:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.70,0:09:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼從這裡蒙混過去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.50,0:09:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個外國人帶著徽章的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.80,0:09:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接問問他現在在哪里不就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.00,0:09:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果呼叫的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.70,0:09:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就有被犯人發現的危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.60,0:09:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然不解開P&A之謎就不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.30,0:10:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是指車子去的目的地呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.40,0:10:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是飯和冰激淩 是飯店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.00,0:10:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是指頭型 也許是美容院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.19,0:10:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.90,0:10:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能認真一點地想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.30,0:10:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.50,0:10:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水鳥和海豹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.70,0:10:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是指動物園嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.80,0:10:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯先生不是喜歡動物嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.40,0:10:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是動物園的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.50,0:10:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沾血的地方就應該是Animal show的Animal了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣 原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了不起 步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.20,0:10:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.00,0:10:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯先生所在的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.60,0:10:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人乘坐的是警車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.60,0:10:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.20,0:10:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天黑之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.30,0:10:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不早一點抓到的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.50,0:10:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會讓他們跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.90,0:10:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由美 怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.00,0:11:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到柯南所說的綁架犯了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.70,0:11:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綁架犯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.90,0:11:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.30,0:11:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南說他們坐在警車上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.40,0:11:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.60,0:11:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.40,0:11:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯先生給我們留下的資訊P&A的暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.60,0:11:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是指警車的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.30,0:11:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.50,0:11:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼說P&A是警車呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.00,0:11:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把P&A裡的&用字母表示試著排列一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P&A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.10,0:11:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P和AND和A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.50,0:11:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PANDA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.80,0:11:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是熊貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.30,0:11:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.80,0:11:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警車的顏色就是白色和黑色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.70,0:11:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以這就是熊貓的原因 原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.80,0:12:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實會有日本警察把警車叫做熊貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.30,0:12:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 被綁架的應該是英籍美國人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.10,0:12:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外國人應該不會知道日本警察的行話呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.70,0:12:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.80,0:12:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使不是警車的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.40,0:12:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要是車身帶有黑白色紋的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不都像熊貓嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.00,0:12:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.30,0:12:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如說是那時外國人能看到熊貓的書也說不定呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.20,0:12:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.70,0:12:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因為被綁架的詹姆斯先生是在倫敦長大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.70,0:12:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說警車是沒錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.60,0:12:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前英國的警車的車身也是被塗為黑色和白色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.60,0:12:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個就是1965年由英國警察第一次引進的叫熊貓的警車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.70,0:12:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警車就等於熊貓 這在英國人的心裡已經紮根了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.30,0:12:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在英語的字典裡面也有熊貓車這一說法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.50,0:12:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 年輕的英國人可能不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那個時代生活過的詹姆斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.00,0:13:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一看見警車應該就馬上會聯想到熊貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.30,0:13:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼時代的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.80,0:13:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.60,0:13:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛巧有一輛警車過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.00,0:13:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是車上乘坐了什麼外國人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.70,0:13:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,車上坐的警官 沒什麼可疑的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.40,0:13:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實是有兩名警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.70,0:13:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在嫌疑犯的頭上蒙著大衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.90,0:13:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在後面的座位上 把嫌疑犯夾在中間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.40,0:13:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就 就是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.60,0:13:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輕而易舉 輕而易舉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.00,0:13:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就按你的計畫在日落之前到達群馬縣的深山裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.70,0:13:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是你的完美計畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.60,0:13:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要掉以輕心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.20,0:14:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得可疑嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.40,0:14:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普通的交通疏導警 卻在一輛一輛車地檢查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.30,0:14:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道 我們已經暴露了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.40,0:14:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那倒不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.30,0:14:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們抓錯了人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.60,0:14:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了以防萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.00,0:14:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先用槍頂住他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.40,0:14:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果等一下再有奇怪地盤查的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.70,0:14:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強行突破吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有 有點不妙啊 佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.00,0:14:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡已經是崎玉縣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.50,0:14:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經讓崎玉縣的警官進行盤查了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.30,0:14:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不用特意地追查也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.30,0:14:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你不擔心嗎 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.40,0:15:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個警車已經由由美檢查了一遍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.60,0:15:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果事情暴露的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.50,0:15:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們就有可能會在被盤查的時候以人質進行要脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.70,0:15:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且在由美檢查的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.30,0:15:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個外國人也是一動不動的沒有反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.20,0:15:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說犯罪集團持有武器的可能性相當高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.80,0:15:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.20,0:15:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攜帶了手槍作武器的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.80,0:15:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在被盤查的時候如果對人質不利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.30,0:15:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.30,0:15:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我就一直在想要如何使犯人在不注意地情況下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.50,0:15:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他們包圍起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.20,0:15:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那種像魔法一樣的辦法能有嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.30,0:15:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種辦法的話 不是沒有的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.60,0:15:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.80,0:15:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偵探團徽章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.00,0:15:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.60,0:15:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛偷偷地放在這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.90,0:15:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.70,0:16:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那個車子的後面500公尺的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.00,0:16:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有個好辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要試一試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.80,0:16:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能成功的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.60,0:16:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在於是否還有很多警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.50,0:16:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是 一直跟到這個地方來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.90,0:16:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.80,0:16:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由美 你在跟著嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.90,0:16:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.40,0:16:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為好像是我讓犯人跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.60,0:16:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由美 你以前確實是做過崎玉縣的監事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.80,0:16:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是 是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.00,0:16:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死 又是紅燈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.20,0:16:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別著急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.30,0:16:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們不張揚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不會暴露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.90,0:16:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了晚上的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我們的天下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.70,0:17:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀 不好 是警車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.20,0:17:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是被發現了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.80,0:17:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.20,0:17:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把人質當擋箭牌逃走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.60,0:17:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救 救命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.70,0:17:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.20,0:17:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.80,0:17:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.70,0:17:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.70,0:17:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是總廳的高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.00,0:17:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請幫助我們抓住那個綁架犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.00,0:17:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,切 嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.70,0:17:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.40,0:17:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,適當地跟在後面 然後在岔道離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.30,0:17:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.60,0:17:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 上當了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.90,0:17:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.20,0:17:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行得順利嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.60,0:17:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.60,0:17:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行得很順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過不要擔心了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.20,0:18:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.40,0:18:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到岔道的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.50,0:18:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.00,0:18:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼停滯不前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會讓犯人跑掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.00,0:18:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左面不行的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.00,0:18:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就去右面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.50,0:18:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.40,0:18:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右面另有一輛警車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.40,0:18:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.00,0:18:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們從後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.30,0:18:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後面也被警車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.20,0:18:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.70,0:18:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.80,0:18:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們前後左右完全被警車包圍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.10,0:18:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹得不賴嘛 偵探隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.50,0:18:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 我還是叫你福爾摩斯比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.20,0:18:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就和他們拼命吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.00,0:18:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.40,0:18:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有人質呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.50,0:18:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.40,0:19:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當有人一聲令下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.10,0:19:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體車輛同時進行煞車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.30,0:19:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人的身體傾斜的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.10,0:19:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們就會束手就擒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.50,0:19:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這有些粗暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.80,0:19:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但幹得很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.10,0:19:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酷小伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.40,0:19:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家了 得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.70,0:19:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 輕而易舉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.50,0:19:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那下次的聚會是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在總廳集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.90,0:19:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.30,0:19:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果佐藤警官也能來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.30,0:19:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.80,0:19:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.40,0:19:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人質詹姆斯·布蘭克先生在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.30,0:19:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才還在的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.00,0:20:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是很可疑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.60,0:20:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個外國人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.00,0:20:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在進行事件調查之前失蹤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.30,0:20:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒覺得有什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.40,0:20:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.70,0:20:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他像個好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.10,0:20:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在意地只是他的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.20,0:20:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.30,0:20:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是因為布蘭克(黑)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.00,0:20:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 是詹姆斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.00,0:20:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 是詹姆斯·龐德的詹姆斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.40,0:20:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說 倒覺得是個好印象的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.10,0:20:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯·莫里亞提教授
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.90,0:20:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪界的拿破崙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.60,0:20:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,福爾摩斯的夙敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.20,0:20:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫里亞提教授
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.60,0:20:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他開頭的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.60,0:20:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想的只是夏洛克罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.20,0:20:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯只是一個到處都有的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.50,0:20:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.80,0:20:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比這個更擔心地是那個車裡看我們的那個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.70,0:21:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是劫持公共汽車事件裡的一名乘客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.00,0:21:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實在事件調查時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.60,0:21:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫做赤井秀一的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.70,0:22:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.50,0:22:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事前就想好留下了那個暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.40,0:22:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.30,0:22:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們是假警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.90,0:22:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們對我就好像是理所當然得說了日語的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.20,0:22:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們作為警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.70,0:22:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是知道我是能說日語的外國人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.00,0:23:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始也應該至少確認一下姓名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.70,0:23:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.20,0:23:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們明明知道我是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.30,0:23:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻假裝不知道來接近我的可疑的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.00,0:23:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 好像是弄錯人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.80,0:23:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.90,0:23:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我卻大吃一驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.20,0:23:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把那麼長的頭髮一下子剪短了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.90,0:23:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改頭換面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.80,0:23:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被戀人狠狠地甩掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.70,0:23:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是為此特意地把我叫出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.60,0:23:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是想和戀人重歸於好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.30,0:23:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要讓她後悔 把我甩掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.70,0:23:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用血和淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.10,0:23:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個血跡是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.20,0:24:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厲害啊 今天沒睡覺就能推理出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.50,0:24:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.00,0:24:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣 這個手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.70,0:24:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.40,0:24:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搖動的餐廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.70,0:24:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.10,0:24:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魚鱗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.90,0:24:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次 是不可思議的餐館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.50,0:24:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論點什麼 只會來鰻魚飯 啊 很好的餐廳吧
